  encounterName: Great-Value Island
  text: Before you looms a giant warehouse of an island. Not a single scrap of vegetation
    grows in the flat gray desert of stone surrounding a giant, blue roofed metal
    building. The inside is its own climate, air conditioning, fluorescent lights,
    and early 2000's pop songs transport you into a new world. A world with Greater
    Value.
